cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.CL 

This paper is about learning-to-learn optimization algorithms for deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of the proposed algorithms on tasks involving convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and long short-term memory networks (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.AI and cs.NE. The other two sub-categories, cs.CV and cs.CL, are less likely but still relevant to the paper's content.
